[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Over the 730-day synthetic history this produces 2 to 3 TSH observations. Within the 12-month baseline window (`now - 366 days`), there is at most 1 TSH observation. `update_patient_baseline` requires `DEFAULT_BASELINE_MIN_SAMPLES = 4` chronic observations to mark the baseline `"ready"`:
