[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m So the actual suppressed reason for `patient-EUTH-004 / 3016-3` should be `["insufficient_data"]`, not the magnitude/duration/deviation triple shown. The demo's actual qualitative behavior (3 surfaced, 2 suppressed) is right, and the second line (creatinine for EUTH-004) is plausible because EUTH does have quarterly creatinine in the synthetic generator. Only the first line's reasons list is suspicious.
